quran[26{c,v,t}:
69,9,aur firaon aur jo log is se pehlay they aur woh jo ulti bustiyon mein rehtay they sab gunah ke kaam karte they
69,10,unhon ne apne perwar-digaar ke paighambar ki nafarmani ki to khuda ne bhi un ko bara sakht pakra
69,11,jab pani tughyani par aaya to hum ne tum ( logon ) ko kashti mein sawaar karliya
69,12,taakay is ko tumahray liye yadgar banayen aur yaad rakhnay walay kaan usay yaad rakhen
69,13,to jab sor mein aik ( baar ) phoonk maar di jaye gi
69,14,aur zameen aur pahar dono utha liye jayen ge. phir aik bargee toar phore kar barabar kardiye jayen ge
69,15,to is roz ho parney wali ( yani qayamat ) ho parre gi
69,16,aur aasman phatt jaye ga to woh is din kamzor hoga
69,17,aur farishtay is ke kinaroon par ( utar ayen ge ) aur tumahray perwar-digaar ke arsh ko is roz aath farishtay apne suron par uthaiye hon ge
69,18,is roz tum ( sab logon ke samnay ) paish kiye jao ge aur tumhari koi posheeda baat chhupi nah rahay gi
69,19,to jis ka ( aamaal ) nama is ke dahinay haath mein diya jaye ga woh ( dosaron se ) kahe ga ke lijiye mera nama ( aamaal ) prhhiye
69,20,mujhe yaqeen tha ke mujh ko mera hisaab ( kitaab ) zaroor miley ga
69,21,pas woh ( shakhs ) mann manay aish mein hoga
69,22,( yani ) ounchay ( ounchay mehloon ) ke baagh mein
69,23,jin ke meway jhuke hue hon ge
69,24,jo ( amal ) tum ayyaam guzashta mein agay bhaij chuke ho is ke siilay mein mazay se khao aur piyo
69,25,aur jis ka nama ( aamaal ) is ke baen haath mein yaad jaye ga woh kahe ga ae kash mujh ko mera ( aamaal ) nama nah diya jata
69,26,aur mujhe maloom nah ho ke mera hisaabkiya hai
69,27,ae kash mout ( abadd ul aabaad ke liye mera kaam ) tamam krchki hoti
69,28,aaj ) mera maal mere kuch bhi kaam bhi nah aaya
69,29,( haae ) meri saltanat khaak mein mil gayi
69,30,( hukum hoga ke ) usay pakar lau aur taoq pehna do
69,31,phir dozakh ki aag mein jhonk do
69,32,phir zanjeer se jis ki naap sattar gaz hai jakar do
69,33,yeh nah to khuday-e jal shana par imaan lata tha
69,34,aur nah faqeer ke khana khilanay par amaada karta tha
